text: Marie-Pier Beaudet is a retired archer from Canada. Beaudet competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics, 2008 Summer Olympics, and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Marie-Pier BEAUDET She was born on 12 December 1986.Marie-Pier Beaudet == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian archers Category:Olympians for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Quebec City
